{"tid":1573441,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃大仙下邨26歲青年墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-09-16T03:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T14:17:35.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"795fa10cdab6a4140633330c5c54610dc7f517d6","tid":1573441,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"黃大仙下邨龍華樓，早上8時02分，一名男子由高處墮下，倒卧地面，昏迷不醒，其19歲胞妹報警求助，地面遺下一灘血迹，救護員接報到場，將事主送院，惟經搶救後不治，警方調查後獲悉事主姓吳（26歲），相信吳從上址一走廊墮下，警員於現場沒有撿獲遺書，相信事件沒有可疑。死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=9c68f8b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"efa0f754015480b7efaf8dfcc8fe8cb063e7b1c6","tid":1573441,"uid":258429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:59:44.000Z","msg":"又無可疑。。"},{"pid":"13f1561873001d9214c8c9523c02a7f52f27307c","tid":1573441,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"又無可疑呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a2105ce8882f832e4f4f4a0ed7d795eb4cbfdd","tid":1573441,"uid":30367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bd47b655ee3aae98023dab61e27f987710c9fe","tid":1573441,"uid":25108,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"有個妹<br />\n點樣可疑"},{"pid":"e09eda531d862a3677efb6238811b27b0dff1a87","tid":1573441,"uid":60563,"like":2,"dislike"